verbose_text: This signature was defined as the sum of phosphoprotein levels of mTOR, 4E-BP1 (S65, T37 / T46, and T70 RPPA features), P70S6K, and S6 (S235 / S236 and S240 / S244 features) and was previously described in Zhang et al..
evidence: levels of mTOR, 4E-BP1 (S65, T37/T46, and T70 RPPA features), P70S6K, and S6
